      <textAnnotation id="sid-7A900C53-A41F-492B-949B-FF9378350DC3" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-C79D640F-D769-4321-83B4-81D450C1324D" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-0E11397B-376F-45E2-B1A7-DE2C74AB6055" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1. MMID stands for Material ID and CPN stands for Customer Part Number
2. It is an optional step, usually MMID is received. In case MMID is not received, instead CPN is received, the derivation of MMID to CPN will take place.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-1DA97420-4E8D-4A84-99B6-BE732E2A3D70" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1. CBA acquires, records and attaches all appropriate documents for justification.
2. Manual creation of FOC sample is an exceptional scenario
3. IRC scenarios will also be covered as part of no charge order process</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-C607BA5E-146D-496E-9CE6-58C5EC930766" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/87e190e5800648088193185674a9aceb</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-0AE39D79-D1CD-4FB5-AC05-0DC19180F0EB" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/5c0c65a2540c438eadc4d41423e3ef0e</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>My Samples 
(Future of Samples)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-0911988E-BFC4-487B-ADF3-71349FCF0E40" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#99CC00"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#99cc00" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#99cc00" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1.Processes are happening outside of Capture Order and are covered in subsequent L3s
2.Prototype Free of Charge Orders are part of Free of Charge Sample Orders 
3. To keep the End to End and Signavio in synchronization we are changing the L3 code description. This L3 process flow represents Sample Free of Charge Order.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <group categoryValueRef="sid-7eee6381-7a97-44b8-8bcc-eb89e6a4ebeb" id="sid-CAFC35B9-3635-4281-9FD2-4C34ED0F2C0C">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
      </group>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-01B4C3B1-F992-4264-90F7-5B9C9BFEA474" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="true" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="18.0" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="true" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="18.0" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform Process Steward: Nuria, Galceran &lt;nuria.galceran@intel.com&gt;, and BPM Champion: Rebeca, Meza Redondo &lt;rebeca.meza.redondo@intel.com&gt; of any changes that occur within the flow from now onwards so that changes can be accurately reflected within BIC</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
